*fr.EPPressSimulation 5/JMPA: ""
*es.EPPressSimulation 5/JMPA: ""
*it.EPPressSimulation 5/JMPA: ""
*de.EPPressSimulation 5/JMPA: ""
*pt.EPPressSimulation 5/JMPA: ""
*nl.EPPressSimulation 5/JMPA: ""

*EPPressSimulation 0/Off: "
	<</DeviceRenderingInfo <</Type 29 /PressType 0>>>> setpagedevice"
*End
*fr.EPPressSimulation 0/Non: ""
*es.EPPressSimulation 0/Desactivado: ""
*it.EPPressSimulation 0/Off: ""
*de.EPPressSimulation 0/Aus: ""
*pt.EPPressSimulation 0/Não: ""
*nl.EPPressSimulation 0/Uit: ""

*?EPPressSimulation: "
	save
	currentpagedevice /DeviceRenderingInfo 2 copy known 
	{get /PressType 2 copy known {get dup 0 eq {pop (None)}if} 
		{pop pop (Unknown)} ifelse}{pop pop (Unknown)} ifelse = flush
	restore
"
*End
*CloseUI: *EPPressSimulation
*CloseGroup: EPColorSettings


*OpenGroup: EPOtherSettings/Others
*fr.Translation EPOtherSettings/Autres: ""
*es.Translation EPOtherSettings/Otros: ""
